text: Club Atlético (; mostly known as Unión de Santa Fe , CA Unión de Santa Fe or simply Unión) is a sports club from Santa Fe, the capital city of the Santa Fe Province, in Argentina. The club was founded on April 15, 1907 and plays in the Argentine Primera División.A 40 años de la "revolución" , El Litoral, 13 Feb 2015 ==References== Category:1900s establishments in Argentina Category:1907 establishments Category:Argentine football clubs Category:Santa Fe, Argentina
